---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Page: 176
Author: Shankara
---
You have built Your temple in my soul.
When I act, the actions are Your actions.
You have made a home in my body.
Even my senses experience You.
Sleeping, I meditate on You,
and every word I utter
is a prayer to You.
My life is no longer anything
but the worship of You.
